2082be34aa113e90a5eb92ac9755dd16ba9423f","tid":1039559,"uid":8435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T14:49:57.000Z","msg":"Interview係要練<br />\n試下m記又好，7仔又好都試下去見<br />\n唔理做唔做都好<br />\n熟習咗個見工模式就無咁易緊張<br />\n<br />\n同埋呢段時間越唔敢面對，之後就更難衝出去<br />\n做下pt等自己唔好咁摺，對見工都有幫助"},{"pid":"e8d5594a3ba9d2d184281c6c1f19b441113a2b4f","tid":1039559,"uid":58869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T15:49:22.000Z","msg":"乜真係會有親戚笑自己人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a210cf7758e79b7370cf4acd177454ddb3236444","tid":1039559,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8d5594a3ba9d2d184281c6c1f19b441113a2b4f","tid":1039559,"uid":58869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T15:49:22.000Z","msg":"乜真係會有親戚笑自己人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T16:15:12.000Z","msg":"有，仲當面講說話比我父母聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我廢到連累父母又陀衰學校&hellip;唆"}]}